### 3. test get products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/product
Accept: application/json

### 4. test get by id
# copy on of the IDs after post 
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/product/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

### 5. test update
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/product/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop - UPDATED",
  "description": "Frissített leírás",
  "price": 2500.99,
  "category": "Elektronika",
  "stock": 10,
  "imageUrl": "https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/laptop-updated.jpg"
}

### 6. test delete product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/product/{{productId}}

### 7. test delete not existing product
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/product/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json